snippet.title: Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet Gameplay | PS4, XB1, PC
snippet.description:
When you're in the world of Gun Gale Online, you'll have to use everything in your environment to outsmart your opponents.  Check out some of the gameplay footage of Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet and let us know what characters and weapons you'll be using! 

Preorder Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet: http://amzn.to/2w8D8UJ
